Sentencas: To optimize the microstructure of cathode for IT-SOFCs, double layered Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta was fabricated and its performances were evaluated.
Titulo: Effect of enhanced reaction area in double layered Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Two types of symmetric cell with BSCF cathodes were prepared on Ce(0.8)G(0.2)O(1.9) electrolyte pellets using a single continuous process, electrostatic slurry spray deposition.
Titulo: Effect of enhanced reaction area in double layered Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Single layered BSCF cathode was fabricated with a porous layer only, while double layered one was fabricated with a porous layer over a thin dense layer.
Titulo: Effect of enhanced reaction area in double layered Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The polarization resistances at 500 degrees C and the activation energy of double layered BSCF were about 61% and 22% lower than single layered BSCF, respectively.
Titulo: Effect of enhanced reaction area in double layered Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The exchange current density of double layered BSCF was also higher than that of single layered BSCF, suggesting that the larger active area of double layered BSCF cathode is effective in the increase of oxygen reduction reaction rates.
Titulo: Effect of enhanced reaction area in double layered Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
